actions.message:
`In order for the bot to Welcome users and give them a Guest role

1. Creat A Guest role
2. Create a Welcome channel - for the welcomes to be seen

I put it on a serch value for this channel
I also did this for Guest on a searched role.

!welcomeon and !welcomeoff to turn it on or off

The bot has to be higher rank then the guest role.
It must also have access to give ranks. 

It also has to be able to see and talk in the Welcome channel

!announce - also needs an announcements channel.

Both "announcements" and "welcome" need to be spelled exactly
they must also have nothing before or after just whats in " "s

A "bot-log" channel will show any errors with the bot and admin
type stuff. Users Joined and Left ect. I plan to expand this.`
